Appium Setup

Android Studio - tool used for emulator 
Appium Server
Appium Inspector
UIAutomatorViewer



First install android studio for starting your emulator

or

you can connect your real device using QRCode or pass code using pair with WiFi

Start the server using appium server

Start Appium Inspector for inspecting the element

Appium drivers

