xcuitest@4.32.22 
mac2 
espresso 
safari 
gecko 
chromium 


emulator 
real device - samsung a53


adb commands

adb shell dumpsys window | grep -E 'mCurrentFocus' for mac
adb shell dumpsys window | find 'mCurrentFocus'  for windows

adb install path of the application


